name: get vr_copy_logs
sql_command: select top 10 a.*,b.ended from vr_copy_logs.csv a left join vr_copy_log_statuses.csv b on a.id = b.id order by a.id desc;

name: get vr_edit_logs
sql_command: select top 10 a.*,b.ended from vr_edit_logs.csv a left join vr_edit_log_statuses.csv b on a.id = b.id order by a.id desc;

name: get cprm_keys
sql_command: select top 10 * from cprm_keys.csv order by id desc;

name: get mmedia_file_lists.csv
sql_command: select top 10 * from mmedia_file_lists.csv where vol_name like '%%';
